{
  "url": "/cat/apparel",
  "type": "root",
  "h1": "Custom Apparel for Your Team or Event",
  "metaTitle": "Custom Apparel | Perfect Imprints",
  "metaDescription": "Shop custom apparel for teams, events, and uniforms. Bulk orders with embroidery or screen printing. Fast turnaround. Get a quote at Perfect Imprints.",
  "introHtml": "<p>Marketing directors, HR managers, safety coordinators, and business owners all face the same challenge: finding apparel that represents their organization effectively while meeting practical needs. Whether you need uniforms that project professionalism, safety gear that keeps your team visible, or promotional clothing that builds brand recognition, the right custom apparel makes a difference.</p><p>Perfect Imprints offers a wide selection of custom apparel suitable for every scenario. Choose from classic items like the Rugby Polo or Pro-Lite Cap for corporate events, or opt for the Safety Tee and Fleece Gloves for workwear that prioritizes visibility and comfort. Our bandanas (Bandana, Big Bandana, Lil' Bandana) and headwear (The Visor) provide versatile options for giveaways and outdoor events. We also carry specialty items like the BeWell™ Socks and COB Headlamp for health and safety initiatives.</p><p>All apparel can be decorated with your logo using screen printing, embroidery, or full-color heat transfer. We work with you to choose the right decoration method based on fabric, design complexity, and quantity. Minimum order quantities vary by product but are designed to accommodate both small team orders and large-scale distributions.</p>",
  "faqs": [
    {
      "q": "What are the minimum order quantities for custom apparel?",
      "a": "Minimum order quantities vary by product. For most items like t-shirts and polos, the minimum is 12 pieces. For accessories like bandanas or caps, the minimum may be lower, often 6 to 12 units. Contact us for specific product MOQs."
    },
    {
      "q": "Which decoration methods are available for apparel?",
      "a": "We offer screen printing for bold, solid-color designs, embroidery for a professional look on polos and caps, and full-color heat transfer for detailed logos. The best method depends on your fabric and design. We'll recommend the right option."
    },
    {
      "q": "How long does production typically take?",
      "a": "Standard production takes 7-10 business days after artwork approval, plus shipping time. Rush orders may be available for an additional fee. We'll provide a precise timeline when you place your order."
    },
    {
      "q": "Can I get a sample before placing a bulk order?",
      "a": "Yes, we offer samples of blank garments for a nominal fee, which is often credited back on your bulk order. You can also request a decorated proof or mockup to ensure your logo looks perfect."
    },
    {
      "q": "What sizes are available for custom apparel?",
      "a": "Most apparel items range from XS to 3XL, with select styles available up to 5XL. We also offer youth sizes for certain products. Check the product page for specific size charts."
    }
  ],
  "heroAltText": "Custom apparel including polo shirts, caps, and safety tees with embroidered logos for corporate teams and events.",
